[{"question":"So what do you think went wrong here?","answer":"Well, Piers, number one, thank you for having me.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":19,"aSentId":20},{"question":"Why?","answer":"OK.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":92,"aSentId":93},{"question":"What did you feel when you watched those images?","answer":"Well, I felt a huge disappointment.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":140,"aSentId":141},{"question":"Or should she be allowed to lead the life she wants to lead?","answer":"Of course she should lead the life she wants to lead.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":158,"aSentId":159},{"question":"What does that mean?","answer":"It means that public opinion had been driven I think by the saturation coverage on television and all of the commentary, so that most people were directed to believe -- and, you know, I\u0027m sure you wouldn\u0027t deny the fact you were directing people to think this -- that this woman killed her child.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":188,"aSentId":189},{"question":"Jealous?","answer":"Tell me about the -- I also love the fact that even then you could tell that you had this kind of firebrand attitude.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":213,"aSentId":214},{"question":"Was it as simple as that?","answer":"You know, Piers, it\u0027s so complicated.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":236,"aSentId":237},{"question":"When you get criticized, what do you think is the biggest misconception about you?","answer":"Oh, Piers, come on, you\u0027ve been through this, I\u0027m sure.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":282,"aSentId":283},{"question":"How has it come to this?","answer":"Well, yes.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":315,"aSentId":316},{"question":"How did you feel when your wife said this to you?","answer":"Well, I think -- I think you need to remember, too, that she is, from time to time, what\u0027s called a blackout drunk.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":342,"aSentId":343},{"question":"What do you hope to achieve by speaking publicly about this?","answer":"Well, I\u0027ll tell you a few things.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":359,"aSentId":360},{"question":"Is this a short, sharp, shock treatment that you have implemented here?","answer":"I won\u0027t rule any of those things out right now.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":381,"aSentId":382},{"question":"What is it that you say that keeps you all going?","answer":"I think that we have certain things that were instilled in us from my mother and my father as we grew up.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":429,"aSentId":430},{"question":"Now, who are you closest to, would you say?","answer":"I would say I\u0027m closest to Billy.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":439,"aSentId":440},{"question":"Do you think he\u0027s serious about this kind of stuff?","answer":"I think that you have been caught in the -- like many other people, in this web, because I think it has always been a plan of his.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":472,"aSentId":473},{"question":"It\u0027s all about you, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"Of course, at the end of the day.","docId":"110722pmt","qSentId":490,"aSentId":491}]